{"nodes": [{"id": "ai_broker_consenso_multi_llm_deterministic_coordinator", "label": "Coordinador determinista", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "AI_Broker_consenso_multi_LLM.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Separa la decisi\u00f3n determinista (c\u00f3digo Python) del \u00e1rbitro sem\u00e1ntico (LLM) para que el consenso sea auditable: valida, selecciona modelos de una allowlist, aplica l\u00edmites de coste/tiempo, persiste, reintenta y cancela, evitando que un LLM controle directamente llamadas HTTP, reintentos o gasto."}, {"id": "ai_broker_consenso_multi_llm_semantic_arbiter", "label": "\u00c1rbitro sem\u00e1ntico", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "AI_Broker_consenso_multi_LLM.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "El LLM analiza el trabajo, propone plan/r\u00fabrica y sintetiza, pero nunca orquesta llamadas, reintentos ni gasto directamente; el coordinador determinista impone allowlists, l\u00edmites y validaci\u00f3n de esquema para mitigar prompt injection y exfiltraci\u00f3n."}, {"id": "ai_broker_consenso_multi_llm_consensus_protocol", "label": "Protocolo de consenso (6 etapas)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "AI_Broker_consenso_multi_LLM.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "ai_broker_consenso_multi_llm_moa_fast", "label": "mixture_of_agents/fast", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "AI_Broker_consenso_multi_LLM.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "ai_broker_consenso_multi_llm_moa_slow", "label": "mixture_of_agents/slow", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "AI_Broker_consenso_multi_LLM.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id